headline: Emerson to Present at J.P. Morgan U.S. All Stars Conference
summary: Emerson (NYSE: EMR) today announced President and Chief Executive Officer Lal Karsanbhai and Chief Financial Officer Mike Baughman will present at the J.P. Morgan U.S. All Stars Conference on Tuesday, September 16th in London, England. The presentation will begin at 2:00 p.m. British Summer Time, 8:00 a.m. Central Time.
